[p]Hello folks,[/p][p][/p][p]The release of [i]All Under Heaven[/i] is just a few days away, and we want to share the changelog ahead of time to give you an idea of what to expect once the update goes live. We're also including a release schedule so you can tell what date/time [i]All Under Heaven[/i] will release for you.[/p][p][/p][p]All of us at Studio Black, here in Stockholm, are so excited to share this with you. [i]All Under Heaven[/i] might just be the biggest expansion we've made for Crusader Kings 3. Growing the map by roughly 30% has definitely had its challenges, but it's been a long-term ambition of ours to establish a complete map of the Old World as a base to build on. While working on adding east Asia, we've had the chance to meet and talk with so many members of our community. [i]All Under Heaven[/i] flourished with the aid of so many useful insights, and so much fruitful collaboration with our fans. We have a lot to thank you all for.[/p][p]The accompanying 1.18.0 free update for the base game is called ‘Crane’. For the cultures we’ve striven to represent in-game, the beloved crane symbolizes happiness, longevity, and the connection between heaven and our mortal world.[/p][p][/p][p]We hope that you all will have as great a time playing [i]All Under Heaven[/i] as we did creating it![/p][p][/p][p]Signed,[/p][p][i]Alexander Oltner[/i], Game Director[/p][p][i]Henrik Lohmander[/i], Design Lead[/p][p][i]Lucia Dzediti[/i], Producer[/p][p][i]Daan Broekhof[/i], Programmer / Code Owner[/p][p][i]Jacob Blakey[/i], Community Manager[/p][p]and everyone else at Paradox Studio Black and Paradox Interactive[/p][p][/p][p][img src="{STEAM_CLAN_IMAGE}/36033026/93773b3e18a8b28e454db9a2425d46a92cfd0a9e.png"][/img][/p][p]
[/p][p][img src="{STEAM_CLAN_IMAGE}/36033026/979ce25c71afcbe2f93a8546727b53e19db16b8b.png"][/img][/p][h3]Unfortunately, the changelog exceeds the character limit for a Steam post![/h3][p][url="https://forum.paradoxplaza.com/forum/threads/all-under-heaven-release-schedule-changelog.1864262/"]You can read the full changelog by following this link to our forums[/url].[/p][p] [/p][p]As a reminder: This update is [b]NOT live[/b] yet![/p][p]  [/p][hr][/hr][p][/p][p][dynamiclink href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3315530/Crusader_Kings_III_All_Under_Heaven/?snr=1_16_16_18_1059&curator_clanid=36033026"][/dynamiclink][/p][p][dynamiclink href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3486700/Crusader_Kings_III_Chapter_IV/?snr=1_16_16_18_1059&curator_clanid=36033026"][/dynamiclink][/p]